# sbt is frequently crashing with out of metaspace space. This may be due to the classes
# generated by the scala compiler which maybe be kept in memory forever. These options should help.
#-J-XX:+UseConcMarkSweepGC
#-J-XX:+CMSClassUnloadingEnabled
# Java 8
#-J-XX:MaxMetaspaceSize=512m
# Java 7
#-J-XX:MaxPermSize=512m

# https://blog.codecentric.de/en/2014/01/useful-jvm-flags-part-8-gc-logging/ 
#-J-verbose:gc
-J-XX:+PrintGCDetails
#-J-Xloggc:gc.log